OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cboy, 17, killed in suspected stabbing
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a 17-year-old boy was
OL,8,Fkilled in a suspected stabbing in
OL,9,Fsouth-west London.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to reports of a
OL,12,Fstabbing after a "potential
OL,13,Faltercation" on Glycena Road,
OL,14,FBattersea, in the early hours of
OL,15,FSaturday morning, the Metropolitan
OL,16,FPolice said.
OL,26,@tD@ROUuD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
