OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781999280
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cboy, 17, killed in suspected stabbing
OL,6,FPolice went to the scene after the
OL,7,Fcall at 4.20am, alongside paramedics
OL,8,Fand an air ambulance where they found
OL,9,Fthe 17-year-old, who was seriously
OL,10,Finjured.
OL,12,FDespite the efforts of paramedics, he
OL,13,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,15,FHis next-of-kin have been informed and
OL,16,Fare being supported by specialist
OL,17,Fofficers, Scotland Yard said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
