CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781999280
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cboy, 17, killed in suspected stabbing
OL,6,FPolice have launched a murder
OL,7,Finvestigation and officers are in the
OL,8,Fsurrounding area, with a large crime
OL,9,Fscene still in place and surrounding
OL,10,Froads closed, the force said on
OL,11,FSaturday afternoon.
OL,13,FNo-one has been arrested so far.
OL,15,FOfficers are appealing for witnesses
OL,16,Fand in particular want to speak to
OL,17,Fanyone who saw a group of males
OL,18,Frunning in Lavender Hill between 4am
OL,19,Fand 5am on Saturday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
