CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781999280
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cboy, 17, killed in suspected stabbing
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Brian Howie,
OL,7,Fsenior investigating officer for the
OL,8,FMet's Specialist Crime Command, said:
OL,9,F"Our inquiries are progressing
OL,10,Fintensively, and our thoughts remain
OL,11,Ffirmly with the victim's family at
OL,12,Fthis extremely difficult time.
OL,14,F"I understand this incident will cause
OL,15,Fsignificant concern within the
OL,16,Fcommunity. There is a continued and
OL,17,Fhighly visible police presence in the
OL,18,Farea, and I would encourage anyone
OL,19,Fwith concerns to approach officers at
OL,20,Fthe scene.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781999280
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cboy, 17, killed in suspected stabbing
OL,6,F"This is a critical stage of the
OL,7,Finvestigation and I am appealing
OL,8,Fdirectly to the public: if you were in
OL,9,Fthe Lavender Hill area between 4am and
OL,10,F5am, specifically Glycena Road,
OL,11,FAcanthus Road or Pountney Road, and
OL,12,Fwitnessed a group of males running,
OL,13,Fplease come forward.
OL,15,F"Any information, no matter how minor
OL,16,Fit may seem, could prove crucial.
OL,17,FCCTV, doorbell or mobile phone footage
OL,18,Fmay provide vital evidence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781999280
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cboy, 17, killed in suspected stabbing
OL,6,F"I would also urge members of the
OL,7,Fpublic not to assume that information
OL,8,Fhas already been shared, any detail
OL,9,Fcould be of significant importance to
OL,10,Fthe investigation."
OL,12,FAnyone with information or footage is
OL,13,Fasked to contact police on 101,
OL,14,Fquoting CAD 1567/20JUN26.
OL,15,FAlternatively, information can be
OL,16,Fprovided anonymously via Crimestoppers
OL,17,Fon 0800 555 111.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@SO]
